UPDATE_SQL:
update xip_pub_mnu_tree
SET NAME=${NAME},
    NODE_TYPE=${NODE_TYPE},
    NODE_ORDER=${NODE_ORDER},
    FUN_TREE_ID = (select FUN_TREE_ID from xip_pub_fun_tree where FUN_TREE_CODE=${FUN_TREE_CODE})
where MNU_TREE_CODE = ${MNU_TREE_CODE}
  and MNU_GROUP_ID =(select MNU_GROUP_ID from xip_pub_mnu_group where MNU_GROUP_CODE=${MNU_GROUP_CODE})

SELECT_SQL:
SELECT 
  (SELECT 
    t.MNU_TREE_CODE 
  FROM
    xip_pub_mnu_tree t 
  WHERE t.MNU_ID = l.MNU_ID) MNU_TREE_CODE,
  (SELECT 
    g.MNU_GROUP_CODE 
  FROM
    xip_pub_mnu_group g 
  WHERE g.MNU_GROUP_ID = l.MNU_GROUP_ID) MNU_GROUP_CODE,
  l.FUN_CODE,
  l.FUN_LANG,
  l.FUN_LANG_VAL 
FROM
  XIP_PUB_MENUGROUP_LANGUAGE l
INSERT_SQL:
INSERT INTO XIP_PUB_MENUGROUP_LANGUAGE 
  (
    MNU_ID,
    MNU_GROUP_ID,
    FUN_CODE,
    FUN_LANG,
    FUN_LANG_VAL
  ) 
VALUES
  (
    (SELECT t.MNU_ID FROM xip_pub_mnu_tree t WHERE t.MNU_TREE_CODE = ${MNU_TREE_CODE} AND t.MNU_GROUP_ID = (SELECT p.MNU_GROUP_ID FROM xip_pub_mnu_group p WHERE p.MNU_GROUP_CODE = ${MNU_GROUP_CODE})),
    (SELECT mp.MNU_GROUP_ID FROM xip_pub_mnu_group mp WHERE mp.MNU_GROUP_CODE = ${MNU_GROUP_CODE}),
    ${FUN_CODE},
    ${FUN_LANG},
    ${FUN_LANG_VAL}
  )

  (select MNU_TREE_CODE from xip_pub_mnu_tree where MNU_ID = t.UP_ID) AS UP_MNU_CODE

where t.MNU_TREE_CODE is not null
  and (t.UP_ID is not null and t.UP_ID <> '-1')

  and MNU_GROUP_ID= (select MNU_GROUP_ID from xip_pub_mnu_group where MNU_GROUP_CODE = ${MNU_GROUP_CODE})

from xip_pub_params pa
where pa.PARAM_TYPE = 'S'
INSERT_SQL: insert into xip_pub_params(PARAM_ID,PARAM_CODE,PARAM_NAME,DESCRIPTION,PARAM_TYPE,ENABLE_FLAG,VAL_SET_CODE,VAL_SQL,CREATION_DATE,VAL_LEVEL)VALUES(${sys.uuid},${PARAM_CODE},${PARAM_NAME},${DESCRIPTION},${PARAM_TYPE},${ENABLE_FLAG},${VAL_SET_CODE},${VAL_SQL},${sys.date},${VAL_LEVEL})
UPDATE_SQL:
update xip_pub_params
set PARAM_NAME=${PARAM_NAME},
    DESCRIPTION=${DESCRIPTION},
    PARAM_TYPE=${PARAM_TYPE},
    ENABLE_FLAG=${ENABLE_FLAG},
    VAL_SET_CODE=${VAL_SET_CODE},
    VAL_SQL=${VAL_SQL},
    LAST_UPDATE_DATE=${sys.date},
    VAL_LEVEL = ${VAL_LEVEL}
where PARAM_CODE=${PARAM_CODE}

l.TMP_L_ID,

l.COLUMN_CODE,
l.COLUMN_NAME,
l.COLUMN_WIDTH,
l.L_DESC,
l.ATTRIBUTE1,
l.ATTRIBUTE2,
l.ATTRIBUTE3,
l.ATTRIBUTE4,
l.ATTRIBUTE5,
l.ATTRIBUTE6,
l.ATTRIBUTE7,
l.ATTRIBUTE8,
l.ATTRIBUTE9,
l.ATTRIBUTE10,
l.CREATION_DATE,
l.CREATED_BY,
l.LAST_UPDATE_DATE,
l.LAST_UPDATED_BY,
l.LAST_UPDATE_LOGIN
FROM
XIP_PUB_IO_TMP_L   l
INSERT_SQL:
insert into XIP_PUB_IO_TMP_L(TMP_L_ID,TMP_H_ID,COLUMN_CODE,COLUMN_NAME,COLUMN_WIDTH,L_DESC,ATTRIBUTE1,ATTRIBUTE2,ATTRIBUTE3,ATTRIBUTE4,ATTRIBUTE5,ATTRIBUTE6,ATTRIBUTE7,ATTRIBUTE8,ATTRIBUTE9,ATTRIBUTE10,CREATION_DATE,CREATED_BY)
values(${sys.uuid},
(select TMP_H_ID from XIP_PUB_IO_TMP_H where TMP_H_CODE =${TMP_H_CODE}),
${COLUMN_CODE},${COLUMN_NAME},${COLUMN_WIDTH},${L_DESC},${ATTRIBUTE1},${ATTRIBUTE2},${ATTRIBUTE3},${ATTRIBUTE4},${ATTRIBUTE5},${ATTRIBUTE6},${ATTRIBUTE7},${ATTRIBUTE8},${ATTRIBUTE9},${ATTRIBUTE10},${sys.date},${CREATED_BY})
UPDATE_SQL:
update XIP_PUB_IO_TMP_L
set
COLUMN_NAME=${COLUMN_NAME},
COLUMN_WIDTH=${COLUMN_WIDTH},
L_DESC=${L_DESC},
ATTRIBUTE1=${ATTRIBUTE1},
ATTRIBUTE2=${ATTRIBUTE2},
ATTRIBUTE3=${ATTRIBUTE3},
ATTRIBUTE4=${ATTRIBUTE4},
ATTRIBUTE5=${ATTRIBUTE5},
ATTRIBUTE6=${ATTRIBUTE6},
ATTRIBUTE7=${ATTRIBUTE7},
ATTRIBUTE8=${ATTRIBUTE8},
ATTRIBUTE9=${ATTRIBUTE9},
ATTRIBUTE10=${ATTRIBUTE10}
where TMP_H_ID=(select TMP_H_ID from XIP_PUB_IO_TMP_H where TMP_H_CODE =${TMP_H_CODE})
  and COLUMN_CODE=${COLUMN_CODE}
